          "Authors": "The Hinode EIS Consortium: Mullard Space Science Laboratory, University College London (UK); Rutherford Appleton Laboratory (UK); Naval Research Laboratory (USA); NASA Goddard Space Flight Center (USA); NASA Marshall Space Flight Center (USA); Japan Aerospace Exploration Agency (Japan); National Astronomical Observatory of Japan (Japan)",
